2. cs.SI (Signal Processing) is also likely as the paper deals with the transmission of signals over channels with state information. 
3. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possibility as the paper may involve analyzing the computational complexity of the coding schemes used. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the paper may involve the transmission of multimedia data over channels with state information. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is a possibility as the paper may involve the analysis of communication networks with state information.
